Christopher V. Powala  Co-Founder and Chief Operating Officer, Aclaris Therapeutics, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 3 different industries.58$2,175,995As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Christopher V. Powala co-founded Aclaris Therapeutics, Inc. in July 2012 and has been its Chief Operating Officer since July 2012. Mr. Powala co-founded Vicept Therapeutics, Inc. in 2009 and served as its Chief Operating Officer. He served as Vice President of Regulatory Affairs & Clinical Operations of Vital Therapies, Inc. He has over 23 years of experience in the pharmaceutical industry and over 20 years in regulatory affairs and drug development. Prior to Vital ... Therapies, he served positions in formulation development and regulatory affairs with Wyeth Laboratories, Inc. Mr. Powala served as a Vice President of Drug Development and Regulatory Affairs at CollaGenex Pharmaceuticals.Read Full Background




