Job Details
               Aclaris Therapeutics, Inc., started by the founders of Vicept Therapeutics, is a privately held specialty pharmaceutical dermatology company focused on the development of novel dermatologic therapies. The company's mission is to develop the first effective topically applied therapy directed toward the removal of seborrheic keratosis and other verrucoid disorders of the skin. The company is also pursuing the development of topical agents for the treatment and prevention of a number of medical and cosmetic indications.
