Mr. Powala is the Chief Operating Officer at Aclaris with over 27 years of experience in the pharmaceutical industry.
Prior to joining Aclaris, Mr. Powala was a co-founder and the Chief Operating Officer of Vicept Therapeutics, Inc., which was acquired by Allergan, Inc. in 2011. Mr. Powala also served as the Vice President of drug development and regulatory affairs at CollaGenex Pharmaceuticals, Inc. and held various positions in product formulation and regulatory affairs at Wyeth Laboratories, Inc.



